Key Match Events: Ausar breaks down the defense and Harris knocks down the open corner C&S 3P.
Cade with a crafty left hand scoop finish.
Sasser ends the quarter with a bucket after back-to-back 3PM from NAW and Reid.
Cade takes and makes a confident shot mid 3rd quarter to answer ANT.
Beasley makes a big-time steal on ANT in the 4th quarter.
Pre-Game Insights: JB goes with Ausar instead of Moore Jr. in the starting lineup.
They are 1-5 on the 2nd night of back-to-backs coming into this game.
Post-Match Reflections: Very impressive performance as they answered every single time the Timberwolves tried to get back in the game.
We haven’t seen them keep a team at 'arms length' like this many times this year.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Ausar making some big-time hustle plays to start the game.
Beasley has struggled from the 3P line in his last two games but makes a tough one off the bounce for his first make of this game.
Gobert changes the trajectory of many shot attempts.
McDaniels making shots for the Timberwolves is a huge difference maker.
